Xiao Yao.

23
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:08,940
Xiao Yao, are you okay?

24
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:11,470
I'm okay.

25
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:23,190
Xiao Yao,

26
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:25,040
